text: Ronald Gene Dunn (born June 1, 1953) is an American musician. He was born in Coleman, Texas. He is a member of the duo Brooks & Dunn. In 2011 he had a "top 10" song on Hot Country Songs music chart. ==Related pages== *List of country musicians from Texas ==Sources== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:American country singers
title: Ronnie Dunn
